article_title: What Can Go Wrong With A Private Health Insurance Exchange? A Lot

article_metadata.author: John C. Goodman

og.description: The fastest growing part of the health insurance market these days is the private exchange. About 6 million workers selected their health plans through private exchanges this year, double last year’s number. The consulting firm Accenture predicts 40 million will do so by 2018.
